data.title: Karakteristike Podizne Platforme Upright TL 49
data.meta_description: Karakteristike podizne platforme Upright TL 49 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides specifications for the TL49K trailer mount boom lift. It has a maximum working height of 17 meters and outreach of 9.1 meters. The lift has a 200kg/2 person platform capacity. It features an articulating telescopic boom with a 1.3 meter 140 degree jib and 90 degree powered platform rotation. The lift has hydraulic outriggers and is designed for rugged use. It can be powered by 24V batteries or 230V mains power.
